org.eclipse.scada.configuration.security.util

Class SecurityAdapterFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • AdapterFactoryImpl
      • org.eclipse.scada.configuration.security.util.SecurityAdapterFactory
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    SecurityItemProviderAdapterFactory

    public class SecurityAdapterFactory
extends AdapterFactoryImpl
    The Adapter Factory for the model. It provides an adapter createXXX method for each class of the model.
    See Also:
    SecurityPackage

      • isFactoryForType

        public boolean isFactoryForType(java.lang.Object object)
        Returns whether this factory is applicable for the type of the object. This implementation returns true if the object is either the model's package or is an instance object of the model.
        Returns:
        whether this factory is applicable for the type of the object.
